                         "content":  "\u003cdiv style=\u0027display:flex;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 12px;margin-bottom:8px\u0027\u003e\u003cspan style=\u0027color:#fbbf24;font-weight:bold\u0027\u003e이지오토 (EasyAuto)\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DXGl3JxDxfSfGdy__dacOEl4x7gfNvMN/view?usp=sharing\u0027 target=\u0027_blank\u0027 style=\u0027color:#a855f7;text-decoration:underline;font-size:13px\u0027\u003e다운로드\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\u0027color:#333\u0027\u003e|\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://youtu.be/QI1mSkss9S8?t=3196\u0027 target=\u0027_blank\u0027 style=\u0027color:#a855f7;text-decoration:underline;font-size:13px\u0027\u003e사용법 최종\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\u0027color:#333\u0027\u003e|\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://youtu.be/ANRdnMZ0b84\u0027 target=\u0027_blank\u0027 style=\u0027color:#a855f7;text-decoration:underline;font-size:13px\u0027\u003e사용법 영상\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp style=\u0027margin-bottom:12px\u0027\u003e이지오토는 그록, 젠스파크, Flow의 이미지/비디오 생성을 자동화해주는 프로그램입니다.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv style=\u0027display:flex;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 12px;margin-bottom:8px;border-top:1px solid #333;padding-top:12px\u0027\u003e\u003cspan style=\u0027color:#fbbf24;font-weight:bold\u0027\u003e이지워크 (EasyWork)\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://easy-work-gamma.vercel.app/\u0027 target=\u0027_blank\u0027 style=\u0027color:#a855f7;text-decoration:underline;font-size:13px\u0027\u003e사이트 바로가기\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\u0027color:#333\u0027\u003e|\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://youtu.be/q3vESpsTM3Y\u0027 target=\u0027_blank\u0027 style=\u0027color:#a855f7;text-decoration:underline;font-size:13px\u0027\u003e설명 영상\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp style=\u0027margin-bottom:0\u0027\u003e이지워크는 이지비디오와 연동하여 반복 작업을 자동화하는 워크플로우 도구입니다.\u003c/p\u003e"
